---
import InvestLayout from '../layouts/InvestLayout.astro';
import PricingTable from '../components/PricingTable.astro';
import Disclosure from '../components/Disclosure.astro';
---

<InvestLayout
  title="Business Model"
  titleVi="Mô hình kinh doanh"
  description="Nguyen AI Computer business model: 8 subscription plans from free to enterprise, with multiple revenue streams and strong unit economics."
>
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gold-gradient">Business Model</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xl text-ink-muted" lang="vi">Mô hình kinh doanh</p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-muted max-w-3xl">
      Subscription-based SaaS with eight tiers — from free entry to enterprise custom contracts. Multiple revenue streams create diversification.
      <span class="block mt-2" lang="vi">SaaS đăng ký với tám gói — từ miễn phí đến doanh nghiệp tùy chỉnh. Nhiều dòng doanh thu tạo đa dạng hóa.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Pricing table -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">8 Plans (V2 Pricing)</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">8 gói (giá V2)</p>
      <PricingTable />
    </div>

    <!-- Revenue streams -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Revenue Streams</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Dòng doanh thu</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          { name: 'Subscriptions', vi: 'Đăng ký', desc: '8-tier monthly recurring revenue' },
          { name: 'Enterprise contracts', vi: 'Hợp đồng doanh nghiệp', desc: 'Custom pricing, annual, SLA' },
          { name: 'Academy certification', vi: 'Chứng nhận Academy', desc: 'Paid certification programs' },
          { name: 'Chapter licensing', vi: 'Cấp phép hội đồng', desc: 'Nguyen Chapter OS licensing' },
          { name: 'API & platform fees', vi: 'Phí API & nền tảng', desc: 'Developer access, integrations' },
          { name: 'Premium data vault', vi: 'Kho dữ liệu cao cấp', desc: 'Additional storage and compute' },
        ].map((stream) => (
          <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-lg p-5 card-hover">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink">{stream.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-ink-dim" lang="vi">{stream.vi}</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2">{stream.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Unit economics -->
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-ink mb-2">Unit Economics (Hypothesis)</h2>
      <p class="text-gold mb-6" lang="vi">Kinh tế đơn vị (giả thuyết)</p>
      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-bg-border rounded-xl p-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-bg-border">
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Starting price (Personal)</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right font-semibold text-gold">299K VND/mo (~$12/mo)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Mid-tier (Founder)</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right font-semibold text-gold">1.999M VND/mo (~$80/mo)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Top-tier (Chapter)</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right font-semibold text-gold">7.999M VND/mo (~$320/mo)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Enterprise</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right font-semibold text-gold">Custom (annual contract)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Primary market</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right text-ink">Vietnam + global Vietnamese diaspora</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 text-ink-muted">Gross margin (target)</td>
              <td class="py-3 text-right font-semibold text-gold">70%+ (SaaS, cloud infrastructure)</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-ink-dim italic">
          Note: Unit economics are hypotheses based on comparable SaaS benchmarks, not verified financials.
          <span class="block" lang="vi">Lưu ý: Kinh tế đơn vị là giả thuyết dựa trên chuẩn SaaS, không phải số liệu đã xác minh.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12"><Disclosure /></div>
  </section>
</InvestLayout>
